Authelia rules for Ghost:
1. login to admin page - admins only
2. login to admin page - deny all other
3. enter Ghost pages - allow all


  - domain: 'test.example.com'
    policy: 'two-factor'
    subject:
      - 'groupe:admins'
    resources:
      - '^/ghost([/?].*$'

  - domain: 'test.example.com'
    policy: 'deny'
    resources:
      - '^/ghost([/?].*$'

  - domain: 'test.example.com'
    policy: 'public'
